                  </hi>. I am clerk to Thomas Nicholls and another, of King's-court, Lombard-street, the owner of the <hi rend="italic">Intrepid</hi>. The prisoner was ship-keeper, and was allowed 18<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. a day—it was paid to his uncle, but he was allowed food on the ship.</p>
